he 2027 FIFA Women's World Cup.\", \"from\": 1066, \"to\": 1258, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1235, \"end\": 1239, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA_Women's_World_Cup\", \"score\": 0.9999999641665915, \"rank\": 3.583209451961903e-08, \"text\": \"FIFA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA_Women's_World_Cup\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA_Women's_World_Cup\"}, {\"begin\": 1248, \"end\": 1257, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA_World_Cup\", \"score\": 0.9997660980642604, \"rank\": 0.0001992837085667224, \"text\": \"World Cup\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA_World_Cup\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA_World_Cup\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I can not wait to see my teammates and friends.\\\"\", \"from\": 1259, \"to\": 1307, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In May,FIFAwill announce the host of the 2027 Women's World Cup, which means there is potential for this match to be a World Cup host vs. World Cup host match-up if the U.S. and Mexico's joint bid is successful.\", \"from\": 1309, \"to\": 1520, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1487, \"end\": 1493, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexico_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999125930013362, \"rank\": 8.741463925453093e-05, \"text\": \"Mexico\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexico_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mexico_women's_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The friendly at Red Bull Arena has plenty of narratives on its own.\", \"from\": 1522, \"to\": 1589, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Gotham FC plays its home matches at the stadium, and this offseason, signed free agents andUSWNTstars Rose Lavelle, Emily Sonnett, Crystal Dunn and Tierna Davidson, and already had Lynn Williams, Midge Purce and Jenna Nighswonger on its roster.\", \"from\": 1591, \"to\": 1835, \"entities\"